{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/blog/2021/02/01/css.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>flex:1</h2>\n<h3>flex 后面单个值</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>如果为数字,\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">flex:1</code> : <code class=\"language-text\">flex-grow:1; flex-shrink:1; flex-basis:0%</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">flex:2</code> : <code class=\"language-text\">flex-grow:2; flex-shrink:1; flex-basis:0%</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>如果为数字 + 单位\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">flex:100px</code> : <code class=\"language-text\">flex-grow:1; flex-shrink:1; flex-basis:100px</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>flex 后面两个值</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>第2个值是数值，<code class=\"language-text\">flex: 1 2</code> : <code class=\"language-text\">flex-grow:1; flex-shrink:2; flex-basis:0%</code></li>\n<li>第2个值是数字+单位，<code class=\"language-text\">flex: 2 100px</code> : <code class=\"language-text\">flex-grow:1; flex-shrink:1; flex-basis:100px</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>三个值，则分别为 flex-grow，flex-shrink，flex-basis</h3>\n<h2>省略号</h2>\n<h3>单行</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.text</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n  <span class=\"token property\">text-overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ellipsis<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n  <span class=\"token property\">white-space</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nowrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>多行</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.text</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -webkit-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">overflow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-line-clamp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-box-orient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> vertical<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","excerpt":"flex:1 flex 后面单个值 如果为数字,  :   :  如果为数字 + 单位  :  flex 后面两个值 第2个值是数值， :  第2个值是数字+单位， :  三个值，则分别为 flex-grow，flex-shrink，flex-basis 省略号 单行 多行","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2021/02/01/css.html","date":"January 31, 2021"},"frontmatter":{"title":"css","img":"./img/2015-05-11.jpeg","author":["Sylvenas"],"categories":"codes"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2021/02/01/css.html"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}